@node CLEARSTYLETAG

@{U}@{FG Highlight}CLEARSTYLETAG                                                               @{FG Text}@{UU}

Purpose: Clears the current style tag.

Syntax:  @{b}clearstyletag@{ub} [STYLETAG name/S]

Format:  @{U}Parameter@{UU}  @{U}Values to enter@{UU}
         STYLETAG   is the current name of the style tag.

Example: clearstyletag styletag 'paragraph text'

@{" Command Format    " link PageStream3:Help/PGS.MSU/FORM}
