@{U}@{FG Highlight}CUTOBJECT                                                                   @{FG Text}@{UU}

Purpose: Cuts the selected object(s) to the clipboard.

Syntax:  @{b}cutobject@{ub} [STATUS | NOSTATUS]
         [DOCUMENT name/S | WINDOW name/S | OBJECTID number/I]

Format:  @{U}Parameter@{UU}  @{U}Values to enter@{UU}
