Purpose: Deletes a chapter in a document.

Syntax:  @{b}deletechapter@{ub} [CHAPTER name/S | WINDOW name/S] [ALERT]

Format:  @{U}Parameter@{UU}     @{U}Values to enter@{UU}
         CHAPTER       is the document/chapter name. (Default=current)
         WINDOW        is the window name. (Default=current)
         ALERT         opens an alert requester. (Default=off)

Example: deletechapter chapter 'DocumentName:Chapter 3 alert'

@{" Command Format    " link PageStream3:Help/PGS.MSU/FORM}
